The '''Oldsmobile Series 70''' is a [[full-size]] midrange automobile produced by [[Oldsmobile]] between the 1939 and 1950 [[model year]]s.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.oldcarbrochures.com/static/NA/Oldsmobile/1939_Oldsmobile/1939_Oldsmobile_Brochure/1939%20Oldsmobile-32-33.html |title=Directory Index: Oldsmobile/1939_Oldsmobile/1939_Oldsmobile_Brochure |publisher=Oldcarbrochures.com |date= |accessdate=2011-11-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Kimes|first=Beverly|title=standard catalog of American Cars 1805-1942|year=1996|publisher=Krause publications|isbn=978-0-87341-428-9}}</ref>
